卡莉·雷·杰普森 (Carly Rae Jepsen) 成为最新一位与斯库特·布劳恩 (Scooter Braun) 分手的艺术家https://www.nme.com/news/music/carly-rae-jepsen-becomes-latest-artist-to-part-ways-with-scooter-braun-3488494?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=carly-rae-杰普森成为最新与斯库特·布劳恩分手的艺术家Will RichardsFri, 25 Aug 2023 08:15:11 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3488494 <p><img width="2000" height="1269" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/NME_Glastonbury23_CarlyRaeJepsen_AFord-69081.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="卡莉·雷·杰普森" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/NME_Glastonbury23_CarlyRaeJepsen_AFord-69081.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/NME_Glastonbury23_CarlyRaeJepsen_AFord-69081-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/NME_Glastonbury23_CarlyRaeJepsen_AFord-69081-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/NME_Glastonbury23_CarlyRaeJepsen_AFord-69081-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/NME_Glastonbury23_CarlyRaeJepsen_AFord-69081-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/NME_Glastonbury23_CarlyRaeJepsen_AFord-69081-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>她与爱莉安娜·格兰德、黛米·洛瓦托等人一起离开了臭名昭著的音乐经理人</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/carly-rae-jepsen-becomes-latest-artist-to-part-ways-with-scooter-braun-3488494">卡莉·雷·杰普森 (Carly Rae Jepsen) 成为最新一位与斯库特·布劳恩 (Scooter Braun) 分手的艺术家的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1269" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/NME_Glastonbury23_CarlyRaeJepsen_AFord-69081.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="卡莉·雷·杰普森" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/NME_Glastonbury23_CarlyRaeJepsen_AFord-69081.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/NME_Glastonbury23_CarlyRaeJepsen_AFord-69081-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/NME_Glastonbury23_CarlyRaeJepsen_AFord-69081-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/NME_Glastonbury23_CarlyRaeJepsen_AFord-69081-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/NME_Glastonbury23_CarlyRaeJepsen_AFord-69081-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/NME_Glastonbury23_CarlyRaeJepsen_AFord-69081-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/carly-rae-jepsen">，卡莉·雷·杰普森 (Carly Rae Jepsen)</a>成为最新一位与音乐经理斯库特·布劳恩 (Scooter Braun) 分道扬镳的艺术家。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/carly-rae-jepsen-the-loneliest-time-review-3331929">卡莉·雷·杰普森 (Carly Rae Jepsen) – 《最孤独的时光》评论：来自邪教流行英雄的流畅声音</a></strong></li></ul><p>本周，有报道称<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/demi-lovato">黛米·洛瓦托</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">爱莉安娜·格兰德</a>已<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/demi-lovato-and-ariana-grande-part-ways-with-manager-scooter-braun-3486626">与经纪人分道扬镳</a>。他的其他客户包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justin-bieber">贾斯汀·比伯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-guetta">大卫·库塔</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-eyed-peas">黑眼豆豆</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ava-max">艾娃·麦克斯</a>。</p><p>另一位最近离开博朗的艺术家是哥伦比亚歌手 J Balvin，他上个月离开博朗的管理层，加入<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jay-z">Jay-Z</a>的 Roc Nation。</p><p>现在， <a href="https://apnews.com/article/scooter-braun-what-to-know-d5669e8b0fe641dd268c2e2cf88b0e24"><em>美联社</em></a>报道称，杰普森已成为最新离开博朗管理层的人，但没有给出这一决定的理由。</p><p>在有关离职的报道曝光后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/scooter-braun-responds-to-reports-of-artist-splits-im-no-longer-managing-myself-3487154">布劳恩在网上分享了一个开玩笑的回应</a>。在谈到这些报道时，他写道：“突发新闻……我不再管理自己了。” </p><figure id="attachment_2955971" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2955971" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-2955971" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Another-picture-of-Scooter-Braun.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Another-picture-of-Scooter-Braun.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Another-picture-of-Scooter-Braun-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Another-picture-of-Scooter-Braun-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Another-picture-of-Scooter-Braun-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Another-picture-of-Scooter-Braun-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Another-picture-of-Scooter-Braun-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2955971" class="wp-caption-text">斯库特·布劳恩 图片来源：Michael Tran/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> 2008 年，布劳恩在观看了当时 12 岁的比伯在 YouTube 上的表演后帮助他开启了自己的职业生涯，从此开始声名鹊起，并从此为他代理了 15 年。然而，近年来，布劳恩因 <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/taylor-swift-resale-music-back-catalogue-scooter-braun-2818914">明显否认泰勒·斯威夫特的母带录音</a>而面临争议。</p><p>去年有报道称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/scooter-braun-says-he-should-have-handled-taylor-swift-situation-differently-3320781">，这位大亨对自己处理泰勒·斯威夫特母带唱片销售的方式感到后悔</a>。</p><p>两人之间的不和始于 2019 年，当时他通过投资集团 Ithaca Holdings <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-calls-out-scooter-braun-for-manipulative-bullying-after-he-buys-her-back-catalogue-2520900">以 3 亿美元（2.27 亿英镑）收购了她的前唱片公司 Big Machine</a> 。</p><p> 2020 年底，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">斯威夫特</a>确认<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/scooter-braun-reportedly-sells-taylor-swifts-big-machine-masters-2818109">她的过往作品的所有权在两年内第二次易手</a>后，这个故事再次成为头条新闻。她还发表了一份声明，其中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/scooter-braun-reportedly-sells-taylor-swifts-big-machine-masters-2818109">表示母带录音“不会出售给我”</a> ，并证实她相信这笔交易“剥夺了我一生的工作”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/carly-rae-jepsen-becomes-latest-artist-to-part-ways-with-scooter-braun-3488494">卡莉·雷·杰普森 (Carly Rae Jepsen) 成为最新一位与斯库特·布劳恩 (Scooter Braun) 分手的艺术家的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo) 分享杰克·怀特 (Jack White) 和圣文森特 (St. Vincent) 对新专辑《Guts》的建议https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-shares-advice-from-jack-white-and-st-vincent-on-new-album-guts-3488139?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=奥利维亚·罗德里戈分享了杰克·怀特和圣文森特对新专辑胆量的建议Anagricel DuranFri, 25 Aug 2023 08:12:07 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3488139 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Olivia-Rodrigo-Jack-White-and-St.-Vincent.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奥利维亚·罗德里戈、杰克·怀特和圣文森特。图片来源：Joseph Okpako、Kevin Winter 和 Christopher Polk，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Olivia-Rodrigo-Jack-White-and-St.-Vincent.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Olivia-Rodrigo-Jack-White-and-St.-Vincent-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Olivia-Rodrigo-Jack-White-and-St.-Vincent-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Olivia-Rodrigo-Jack-White-and-St.-Vincent-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Olivia-Rodrigo-Jack-White-and-St.-Vincent-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Olivia-Rodrigo-Jack-White-and-St.-Vincent-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “‘你唯一的工作就是写你想在广播中听到的音乐’”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-shares-advice-from-jack-white-and-st-vincent-on-new-album-guts-3488139">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo) 分享杰克·怀特 (Jack White) 和圣文森特 (St. Vincent) 对新专辑《Guts》的建议的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Olivia-Rodrigo-Jack-White-and-St.-Vincent.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奥利维亚·罗德里戈、杰克·怀特和圣文森特。图片来源：Joseph Okpako、Kevin Winter 和 Christopher Polk，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Olivia-Rodrigo-Jack-White-and-St.-Vincent.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Olivia-Rodrigo-Jack-White-and-St.-Vincent-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Olivia-Rodrigo-Jack-White-and-St.-Vincent-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Olivia-Rodrigo-Jack-White-and-St.-Vincent-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Olivia-Rodrigo-Jack-White-and-St.-Vincent-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Olivia-Rodrigo-Jack-White-and-St.-Vincent-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈</a>分享了<a href="/artists/jack-white">杰克·怀特</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/st-vincent">圣文森特</a>在创作她的专辑“Guts”时给她的建议。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/olivia-rodrigo-cover-interview-2021-sour-drivers-license-2940697"><em>NME</em>大读物 – 奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo)：“作为一名歌曲作者，受到认真对待对我来说很重要”</a></strong></li></ul><p>在最近接受<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/08/24/arts/music/olivia-rodrigo-guts.html?smid=nytcore-ios-share&amp;referringSource=articleShare" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《纽约时报》</em></a>采访时，罗德里戈解释了她如何在创作新专辑的压力下向怀特寻求帮助。</p><p> “我第一次见到他时，他给我写了这封信，信中写道，‘你唯一的工作就是创作你想在广播中听到的音乐，’”她说。这位歌手接着补充道：“我的意思是，写出你想在广播中听到的歌曲实际上非常困难。”</p><p>圣文森特是罗德里戈在创作专辑期间与之交谈的另一位音乐家，并将他视为导师。圣文森特（真名安妮·克拉克）在接受<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/08/24/arts/music/olivia-rodrigo-guts.html?smid=nytcore-ios-share&amp;referringSource=articleShare" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《纽约时报》</em></a>电话采访时表示：“我从未见过如此年轻、如此泰然自若的人。 [罗德里戈]知道她是谁，她想要什么——而且似乎一点也不害怕表达出来。而且也是一个非常可爱的女孩，”她补充道。 “我从来没有听她说过任何人的坏话。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cv9PQWNrkzS/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" 