t-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/stormzy-this-is-what-i-mean-review-3355857">《This is What I Mean》</a> 、 <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kendrick-lamar">Kendrick Lamar</a>的<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kendrick-lamar-mr-morale-and-the-big-steppers-3225059">《Mr.》。 Morale &amp; The Big Steppers”</a> 、 <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sbtrkt">SBTRKT</a>的“Evening Glow”以及<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/headie-one">Headie One</a>和<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fred-again">Fred</a>的<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/headie-one-x-fred-again-gang-review-jamie-xx-sampha-slowthai-fka-twigs-octavian-2639727">“Soldiers”</a> 。</p><p> Sampha 的首张专辑《Process》获得了<em>NME</em>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/sampha-process-album-review-1964828">四星评价</a>，Jonny Ensall 写道：“《Process》可能不像 Sampha 在他的创作生涯中参与的其他一些唱片那样大胆、富有创意或改变生活。职业生涯，但它确实有一种适合其制造者的安静、庄严的影响。他还没有走出自己阴暗的背景世界；相反，他邀请我们去那里和他一起去。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sampha-announces-new-album-lahai-3488451">Sampha 宣布新专辑《Lahai》</a>后首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
